"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-04-Vodi-ek-aims-for-gold-in-the-Olympics-fastest-sport-Formula-Kite-1vH9heL1LHO-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pablo Gutierrez in Koper, Slovenia  Copied  Fancy watching a sport that blends surfboards, parachute-like sails, and slender hydrofoils as competitors hurtle along at something like 80 kilometers per hour?\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\", \"score\": 0.9995931220524518, \"rank\": 0.0004070435644917277, \"text\": \"Koper\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"score\": 0.9737996974725005, \"rank\": 0.026896192322959794, \"text\": \"Slovenia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fancy_Crane\", \"score\": 0.999999998662588, \"rank\": 1.3372150988155234e-09, \"text\": \"Fancy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fancy_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fancy_Crane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many do, which is why \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cFormula Kite racing \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 the fastest sport at the Summer Games \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\\u00a0has generated considerable excitement and anticipation ahead of its Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While it's a novelty for some, for Slovenian Formula Kite racer Toni Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek it's an everyday quest.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"score\": 0.97255597101768, \"rank\": 0.028079722318575383, \"text\": \"Slovenian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.192757270855735e-35, \"text\": \"Kite\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under clear blue skies on the vast Mediterranean, Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek catches the morning wind.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As each gust propels him forward, his sleek board slices through the water \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\\u00a0and as he fine-tunes his skills for the upcoming Olympics, he knows precision and agility will be crucial.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cIn his hometown of Koper, where his passion for kiteboarding began, Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek took a break from the water to explore the coastal streets on bicycles with CGTN correspondent Pablo Gutierrez.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\", \"score\": 0.9995931220524518, \"rank\": 0.0004070435644917277, \"text\": \"Koper\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as he geared up for sport's most significant event, the local community was eager to support their hometown hero.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"I know that my sport is not yet massive \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it is growing,\\\" Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek remarked.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just hope to be a good inspiration for the new generation coming up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cVodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek is one of 40 competitors\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009420 men and 20 women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094vying for gold at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will race up to four times daily, aiming for a target time of around 11 minutes on courses approximately 10 kilometers long situated at the Marseille Marina \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 further along the sparkling Mediterranean.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.997257736885898, \"rank\": 0.002749803799647276, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cIs it exciting to be part of a sport breaking through into international prominence, on the biggest stage of all?\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Definitely, it is,\\\" smiled Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whenever I think about it, my heart is pounding, and for the sport to become Olympic, that steps it to the next level.\\\"\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE  Denmark's Mandarin-speaking badminton champ  Refugee team seeks first Olympic medal  Hungarian judo star fights for his sport  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cFormula Kite racing requires exceptional skill, with athletes navigating hydrofoil boards at high speeds.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9999795549400017, \"rank\": 1.989652784669156e-05, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}, {\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999540705, \"rank\": 4.5733405861859275e-11, \"text\": \"Refugee\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee\"}, {\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.7291252116861041, \"rank\": 0.37149668138288755, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They wear helmets, goggles, and impact vests for safety as they maneuver through challenging courses, avoiding obstacles while maintaining top speeds.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cVodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek's journey in kiteboarding began at a young age, under the guidance of his father, Rajko Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek, an accomplished windsurfer who proudly recounted the boy's history of confidently following in his father's footsteps.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2522, \"end\": 2524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin\", \"score\": 0.9995809005317807, \"rank\": 0.00041891966083133363, \"text\": \"ek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At two years, he was skiing,\\\" Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek senior told CGTN.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At three years, snowboarding; at four years, monoskiing, then double skiing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094so many different sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cGuided by his father's expertise, Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek won three successive youth world championships between 2016 and 2018.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022 he became the European and World Champion \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\\u00a0and in 2023, he was the world runner-up.\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2962, \"end\": 2976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"score\": 0.9999906923959556, \"rank\": 9.307628009718631e-06, \"text\": \"World Champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek trains intensively, getting ready for the trials ahead.\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And like all Olympians, he knows it's not merely about muscles and coordination: much of being a champion comes from winning the battle between your own ears.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just physical - mental battles are also hard,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just a one-day, 10-minute regatta - it spans out for five days and a lot of time on the water.\\\"\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if anyone was born for the battle, it's Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and as a global audience watches what for many will be a brand new sport, he's hoping to be the hero of the hour.\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3940, \"entities\": []}]}"